io.gearpump.streaming.appmaster

Class ExecutorManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.gearpump.streaming.appmaster.ExecutorManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    akka.actor.Actor

    public class ExecutorManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements akka.actor.Actor
    ExecutorManager manage the start and stop of all executors.

    ExecutorManager will launch Executor when asked. It hide the details like starting a new ExecutorSystem from user. Please use ExecutorManager.props() to construct this actor
